Had that madman gone and told Giselle exactly what Edwin was thinking?

 "What did that bastard say?"  "Only that."

By the reaction of Giselle and the others, it seemed to be true. At least he knew that if he went around detailing everything he had been told, she would end up looking bad herself. Cunning and repugnant at the same time.

