He recalled the lie that the son-of-a-bitch had shamelessly blurted out.

 "What he said is affecting you, isn't it? That's why you're acting like this."  "It's not true."

Although it lasted an instant, Edwin didn't overlook the flash of unease that clouded Giselle's serene gaze.

