 "Representing the Talon Squad"

It was tradition for the unit's commander to receive the decoration on behalf of all.
Chapter 136.
The public's anticipation, which had been rising in hopes of seeing the Talon Battalion commander, cooled as if hit by a sudden frost the moment the Director of the Military Intelligence Agency stepped onto the platform instead.

The members of the three battalionsSentinel, Ghost, and Talonare kept in absolute secrecy. The same applies to the identity of their commanders. Even in this glorious place where their merits and sacrifices are being recognized.

